\begin_inset Formula $\mu(A\sm B)=0,$
\end_inset

 then if 
\begin_inset Formula $f\in\mathscr{L}^{1}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\i fA{}{\mu}\leq\i fB{}{\mu}.
\]

\end_inset


